quest.2690BF30D8119E77.quest_desc.original:
&eCustom Machinery&r has a built-in structure preview function that allows you to see where the blocks should be placed in the world.

To access this feature, simply click the Recipe arrow inside of the UI, then click the structure block in JEI to see the block placements in the world.

&7&oThe next page contains screenshots to help guide you, and the final page contains a screenshot of the fully-built structure. ->
{@pagebreak}
{image:ftb:textures/quests/ae2/circuit_fabricator_ui.png width:180 height:100 align:center}
{image:ftb:textures/quests/ae2/circuit_fabricator_jei.png width:205 height:144 align:center)
{@pagebreak}
The final structure should look like the picture below, with vibrant quartz glass on all the three sides of the mysterious cube block.

{image:ftb:textures/quests/ae2/circuit_fabricator_full.png width:180 height:150 align:center}

quest.2690BF30D8119E77.quest_desc.translation:
《&e自訂機器&r》內建結構預覽功能，可直接查看方塊在世界中的擺放位置。

使用方式很簡單：先在機器的介面內點選配方箭頭，
再到 JEI 點結構方塊，

就能看到世界中的擺放位置預覽。

&7&o下一頁有引導用擷圖，最後一頁則是完整結構示意圖。->
{@pagebreak}
{image:ftb:textures/quests/ae2/circuit_fabricator_ui.png width:180 height:100 align:center}
{image:ftb:textures/quests/ae2/circuit_fabricator_jei.png width:205 height:144 align:center)
{@pagebreak}
最終結構應如下圖，神秘立方體三個側面，都要放上發光石英玻璃。

{image:ftb:textures/quests/ae2/circuit_fabricator_full.png width:180 height:150 align:center}
